'''Plieto''' (Ingglish: '''Plato''' (pronongx /ˈpleɪtoʊ/; Griik: Πλάτων, Plátōn, "braad", 428/427 BC – 348/347 BC), weha Klasikal [[Griis|Griik]] filasafa, matimatishan, raita a filasafikal dayalag, ah founda a di Akiadimi ina [[Atenz|Atenz]], di fos inschrokshan a aya laanin ina di Westan wol. Wid ih menta, [[Sakratiiz|Sakratiiz]], ah ih schuudent, [[Aristakl|Aristakl]], Plieto elp fi lie di foundieshan a nachral filasafi, sayans, ah Westn filasafi. Plieto weh arijinali schuudent a Sakratiiz, ah weh dis az moch influens bai ih tingkin az bai wa ih si az ih tiicha anjos det.

Plieto safistikieshan az raita wel evident ina ih Sakratik dayalagdem; toti-faib dayalag ah totiin leta chradishanali askraib tu im, alduo madan skalaship dout di aatentisiti a akliis som a dem. Plieto raitndem poblish ina sebral fashin; dis rizolt ina sebral kanvenshan rigyaadn di niemin ah refransin a Plieto texdem.

Alduo no moch piipl kuestian se Plieto lekcha a di Akiadimi we ih foun, di pedagajikal fongshan a ih dayalagdem, ef eni, nobadi no nuo fi soertn. Di dayalagdem sens Plieto taim yuuz fi tiich a rienj a sobjik, muosli ''h''ingkluudn [[Filasafi|filasafi]], [[Lajik|lajik]], rechrik, [[Matimatix|matimatix]], ah adaels sobjik wa ih rait bout.

